# line-string-special-chars

## Input

```
a { port 80 }
b |> combined
c +- signs

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..39
  ENTRY@0..14
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "a"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    LINE_STRING@2..13
      STRING@2..13 "{ port 80 }"
    NEWLINE@13..14 "\n"
  ENTRY@14..28
    WORD_KEY@14..15
      WORD@14..15 "b"
    SPACE@15..16 " "
    LINE_STRING@16..27
      STRING@16..27 "|> combined"
    NEWLINE@27..28 "\n"
  ENTRY@28..39
    WORD_KEY@28..29
      WORD@28..29 "c"
    SPACE@29..30 " "
    LINE_STRING@30..38
      STRING@30..38 "+- signs"
    NEWLINE@38..39 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "a",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@2..13 "{ port 80 }",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@14..15 "b",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@16..27 "|> combined",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@28..29 "c",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@30..38 "+- signs",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

